{"text_id":159976,"tokens":["Summer"," projects"," assigned"," by"," teachers"," can"," be"," a"," contentious"," issue"," among"," students"," and"," parents","."," On"," one"," hand",","," they"," provide"," a"," valuable"," opportunity"," for"," students"," to"," continue"," learning"," and"," practicing"," their"," skills"," outside"," of"," the"," traditional"," classroom"," setting","."," On"," the"," other"," hand",","," they"," can"," add"," undue"," stress"," and"," take"," away"," from"," the"," much","-","needed"," relaxation"," and"," rejuvenation"," that"," summer"," break"," is"," meant"," to"," provide",".","\n\n","When"," it"," comes"," to"," the"," design"," of"," summer"," projects",","," there"," are"," two"," main"," approaches",":"," student","-","designed"," projects"," and"," teacher","-","designed"," projects","."," Student","-","designed"," projects"," allow"," students"," to"," explore"," their"," own"," interests"," and"," passions",","," which"," can"," lead"," to"," a"," more"," engaged"," and"," motivated"," learning"," experience","."," For"," example",","," a"," student"," who"," is"," interested"," in"," marine"," biology"," might"," choose"," to"," design"," a"," project"," around"," ocean"," conservation",","," which"," would"," allow"," them"," to"," delve"," deeper"," into"," a"," topic"," that"," they"," are"," genuinely"," excited"," about","."," This"," approach"," also"," fosters"," critical"," thinking"," and"," problem","-","solving"," skills",","," as"," students"," are"," responsible"," for"," coming"," up"," with"," their"," own"," ideas"," and"," solutions",".","\n\n","However",","," student","-","designed"," projects"," do"," have"," the"," potential"," to"," veer"," off"," track"," and"," become"," more"," of"," a"," hobby"," than"," an"," educational"," experience","."," Additionally",","," without"," proper"," guidance"," and"," structure",","," students"," may"," not"," fully"," grasp"," the"," material"," or"," concepts"," that"," they"," are"," meant"," to"," be"," learning",".","\n\n","Teacher","-","designed"," projects",","," on"," the"," other"," hand",","," provide"," a"," more"," structured"," and"," focused"," learning"," experience","."," Teachers"," can"," ensure"," that"," the"," projects"," align"," with"," the"," curriculum"," and"," that"," students"," are"," learning"," the"," necessary"," material","."," This"," approach"," also"," ensures"," that"," all"," students"," are"," working"," on"," projects"," that"," are"," at"," an"," appropriate"," level"," of"," difficulty"," and"," are"," able"," to"," receive"," consistent"," feedback"," and"," support"," from"," the"," teacher",".","\n\n","However",","," teacher","-","designed"," projects"," may"," not"," allow"," for"," as"," much"," creativity"," and"," personalization"," as"," student","-","designed"," projects","."," Additionally",","," if"," the"," projects"," are"," not"," designed"," well",","," they"," can"," become"," tedious"," and"," uninteresting"," for"," students",","," which"," can"," lead"," to"," dis","engagement"," and"," a"," lack"," of"," motivation",".","\n\n","Another"," important"," factor"," to"," consider"," is"," the"," potential"," for"," forgetting"," learned"," material"," without"," summer"," work","."," Research"," has"," shown"," that"," students"," can"," lose"," up"," to"," ","3","0","%"," of"," their"," academic"," skills"," over"," the"," summer"," months"," if"," they"," do"," not"," engage"," in"," any"," educational"," activities","."," Summer"," projects"," can"," help"," to"," mitigate"," this"," loss"," by"," providing"," students"," with"," opportunities"," to"," continue"," learning"," and"," practicing"," their"," skills",".","\n\n","However",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," strike"," a"," balance"," between"," academics"," and"," enjoyment"," during"," the"," summer"," break","."," Students"," need"," time"," to"," relax",","," recharge",","," and"," engage"," in"," activities"," that"," they"," enjoy",","," such"," as"," spending"," time"," with"," friends"," and"," family",","," participating"," in"," sports"," and"," hobbies",","," and"," traveling","."," Over","loading"," students"," with"," too"," much"," summer"," work"," can"," take"," away"," from"," these"," valuable"," experiences"," and"," lead"," to"," burnout",".","\n\n","In"," my"," personal"," experience",","," I"," have"," had"," both"," positive"," and"," negative"," experiences"," with"," summer"," projects","."," As"," a"," student",","," I"," appreciated"," the"," opportunity"," to"," explore"," my"," own"," interests"," and"," passions"," through"," student","-","designed"," projects","."," However",","," I"," also"," found"," that"," some"," projects"," were"," not"," well","-","designed"," and"," became"," more"," of"," a"," chore"," than"," an"," educational"," experience","."," As"," a"," teacher",","," I"," have"," seen"," the"," benefits"," of"," well","-","designed"," teacher","-","designed"," projects",","," as"," they"," provide"," structure"," and"," focus"," for"," students","'"," learning","."," However",","," I"," also"," understand"," the"," importance"," of"," allowing"," students"," to"," have"," time"," to"," enjoy"," their"," summer"," break"," and"," engage"," in"," activities"," that"," they"," enjoy",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," summer"," projects"," assigned"," by"," teachers"," can"," be"," a"," valuable"," tool"," for"," continuing"," learning"," and"," practicing"," skills"," outside"," of"," the"," traditional"," classroom"," setting","."," However",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," consider"," the"," pros"," and"," cons"," of"," student","-","designed"," projects"," versus"," teacher","-","designed"," projects",","," the"," potential"," for"," forgetting"," learned"," material"," without"," summer"," work",","," and"," the"," impact"," of"," summer"," projects"," on"," students","'"," ability"," to"," enjoy"," their"," break","."," By"," finding"," a"," balance"," between"," academics"," and"," enjoyment",","," summer"," projects"," can"," provide"," a"," meaningful"," and"," engaging"," learning"," experience"," for"," students"," while"," still"," allowing"," them"," to"," enjoy"," their"," much","-","needed"," summer"," break","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}